---
title: "Nadine's Restaurant | German, Austrian & French Cuisine | Yorktown Heights, NY"
description: "Nadine's Restaurant in Yorktown Heights, NY serves traditional German, Austrian, and French dishes in a warm, welcoming atmosphere. Dine in, order online, or book a reservation."
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block head %}
<script id="marketing-popup-script" data-restaurant-id="799" src="https://88restaurants.com/uploads/popup.js"></script>
{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", async () => {
    try {
      const response = await fetch(
        "https://88restaurants.com/restaurants/799/online_orders/discount_button"
      );
      const html = await response.text();
      document.body.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", html);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error("Error fetching button:", error);
    }
  });
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  {# ── HERO ── #}
  <section class="bg-cream overflow-hidden relative">
    {# Fraktur watermark #}
    <span class="hero-watermark font-fraktur leading-none text-amber/10 select-none pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap overflow-hidden md:text-[16rem]">Gemütlichkeit</span>
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-16 md:pt-24 md:pb-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-12 md:gap-16 relative z-10">

      {# Left: text #}
      <div class="flex-1 max-w-xl fade-up">
        <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Yorktown Heights, NY</p>
        <div class="flex gap-1.5 mb-6">
          <span class="text-amber text-lg">&#9670;</span>
          <span class="text-amber text-lg">&#9670;</span>
          <span class="text-amber text-lg">&#9670;</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-tight text-espresso mb-6">
          Traditional Flavors,<br>Warmly <em class="not-italic text-amber">Shared</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-espresso/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          German, Austrian & French cuisine in the heart of Yorktown — crafted with care, served with <em>gemütlichkeit</em>.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="{{ '/menu/' | url }}" class="btn-primary">View Menu</a>
          <a href="#reservations" class="btn-outline">Book a Table</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# Right: image carousel #}
      <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
        <div class="relative w-72 h-72 md:w-96 md:h-96">
          {# Decorative rings #}
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-2 border-amber/40 scale-110"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-amber/20 scale-125"></div>
          {# Images — add/remove <img> tags here as needed #}
          <div id="hero-slides" class="w-full h-full">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/hero-1.png' | url }}" alt="Nadine's Restaurant" class="hero-slide w-full h-full object-contain absolute inset-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 opacity-100">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/hero-2.png' | url }}" alt="Nadine's Restaurant" class="hero-slide w-full h-full object-contain absolute inset-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 opacity-0">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/hero-3.png' | url }}" alt="Nadine's Restaurant" class="hero-slide w-full h-full object-contain absolute inset-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 opacity-0">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="bg-cream overflow-hidden">


    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      {# Mosaic — order-last on mobile so text appears first #}
      <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 h-[480px] lg:h-[560px] fade-up order-last lg:order-first">
        {# plates-1: tall skinny far left, spans full height #}
        <div class="row-span-2 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden col-span-1">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/plates-1.jpg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's dishes" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        {# interior and exterior stacked on the right two columns #}
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden col-span-2">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/interior-1.jpg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's interior" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden col-span-2">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/exterior-1.jpg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's exterior" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>

      {# Text #}
      <div class="flex-1 max-w-xl fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
        <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-espresso mb-6">Welcome to<br>Nadine's</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-espresso/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Christian and Pamela Schienle, along with their son Jagger, have opened Nadine's Restaurant — formerly Jennifer's German Restaurant in Yorktown for over thirty years. The Schienle family have been searching for the perfect location for a sister restaurant to Sel et Poivre in NYC, a French bistro that has been in the family for three decades.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-espresso/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          With Christian being from Vienna, Austria, they crafted a menu combining traditional German dishes with French classics — plus a special dish of the night.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-espresso/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Nadine is Pamela's middle name, and represents their passion for food, hospitality, family and friends — or, as they say in Austria, <span class="font-fraktur text-2xl text-espresso">Gemütlichkeit</span>.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  {# ── MENUS ── #}
  <section class="relative bg-espresso overflow-hidden">
    {# Background image with dark overlay #}
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/images/slide-1.jpg' | url }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15">
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

      {# Heading #}
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Explore</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-cream">Our Menus</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-4">
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
          <span class="text-amber">&#9670;</span>
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# Menu cards — drinks | ALL DAY (featured center) | specials #}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.35fr_1fr] gap-8 fade-up" style="align-items: end;">

        {# Drinks — left #}
        <a href="{{ '/drinks/' | url }}" class="group flex flex-col rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-amber/40 hover:border-amber transition-colors duration-300 md:mb-12">
          <div class="h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/thumbnail-drinks-menu.jpg' | url }}" alt="Bar & Drinks" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col p-6 bg-espresso">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl text-cream mb-2 group-hover:text-amber transition-colors">Bar & Drinks</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-cream/50 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Wines, beers, cocktails & more</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-5 border-t border-cream/10 text-amber font-body font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:text-cream transition-colors">
              View Menu
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        {# All Day Menu — featured center; shown first on mobile #}
        <a href="{{ '/menu/' | url }}" class="group flex flex-col rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-amber/30 hover:border-amber transition-colors duration-300 shadow-2xl order-first md:order-none">
          <div class="h-80 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/thumbnail-main-menu.jpg' | url }}" alt="All Day Menu" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col p-8 bg-espresso">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-4xl text-cream mb-3 group-hover:text-amber transition-colors">All Day Menu</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-cream/50 text-base leading-relaxed flex-1">German, Austrian & French classics — something for every appetite</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-5 border-t border-cream/10 text-amber font-body font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:text-cream transition-colors">
              View Menu
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        {# Specials — right #}
        <a href="{{ '/specials/' | url }}" class="group flex flex-col rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-amber/40 hover:border-amber transition-colors duration-300 md:mb-12">
          <div class="h-56 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/images/thumbnail-specials-menu.jpg' | url }}" alt="Chef's Specials" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col p-6 bg-espresso">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl text-cream mb-2 group-hover:text-amber transition-colors">Daily Specials</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-cream/50 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">Fresh seasonal dishes crafted nightly by our kitchen</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-5 border-t border-cream/10 text-amber font-body font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:text-cream transition-colors">
              View Menu
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="reservations" class="bg-cream relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 lg:pb-36">

      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Join Us</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-espresso mb-4">Reservations</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
          <span class="text-amber">&#9670;</span>
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-stretch gap-12 lg:gap-16">

        {# Image with rounded corners floating over background #}
        <div class="flex-1 w-full fade-up order-last lg:order-first -mb-[168px] lg:mb-0">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/interior-3.jpg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's dining room" class="w-full h-[480px] lg:h-full object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
        </div>

        {# Widget + blurb #}
        <div class="flex-none w-full lg:w-[320px] flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
          <p class="font-body text-espresso/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center lg:text-left">
            We'd love to have you. Book your table below and we'll have everything ready for your visit.
          </p>
          <iframe id="widget" width="300" height="442" src="https://88restaurants.com/799/widgets/302" style="border: none; background: none; border-radius: 5px;"></iframe>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ── BEER GARDEN ── #}
  <section id="beer-garden" class="bg-espresso lg:bg-transparent relative z-10 lg:z-30">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row min-h-[640px] pt-[80px] lg:pt-0 relative">
      {# Desktop espresso bg — starts below the photo bleed area so cream shows through at top #}
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 top-16 bg-espresso -z-10"></div>

      {# Left: text panel (desktop: order-2, pushed right) #}
      <div class="w-fit flex flex-col justify-center px-10 py-24 lg:px-16 relative overflow-hidden lg:order-2">
        {# Content #}
        <div class="relative z-10 fade-up">
          <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Nadine's</p>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-6xl md:text-7xl text-cream mb-6">Biergarten</h2>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
            <span class="text-amber">&#9670;</span>
            <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-body text-cream/70 text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-md">
            Escape to our lush outdoor beer garden — fire pit, fresh air, cold beer, and good company. The perfect spot to unwind after a long week. Open seasonally.
          </p>
          <a href="#reservations" class="btn-outline border-cream/50 text-cream hover:bg-cream hover:text-espresso self-start">Reserve a Table</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {# Collage — desktop: order-1, anchored far left, no padding, bleeds top/bottom #}
      <div class="flex-1 relative min-h-[520px] lg:min-h-0 p-12 lg:p-0 fade-up -mb-[120px] lg:mb-0 lg:order-1" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
        {# Fraktur watermark #}
        <span class="prost-watermark font-fraktur text-amber/20 select-none pointer-events-none absolute lg:top-0 -right-8 bottom-0 flex items-center justify-center" style="writing-mode: vertical-rl; font-size: clamp(8rem, 20vw, 22rem); line-height: 1;">Próst!</span>
        {# Back: top-left, overlapped by middle #}
        <div class="absolute top-4 left-2 w-[55%] h-[50%] lg:-top-16 lg:left-4 lg:w-[48%] lg:h-[52%] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl rotate-[-3deg] border-4 border-cream">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/beer-garden-1.jpeg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's beer garden" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        {# Middle: large, overlaps back, shifted left #}
        <div class="absolute top-48 left-[22%] w-[68%] h-[58%] lg:top-[15%] lg:bottom-auto lg:left-[18%] lg:w-[62%] lg:h-[65%] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl rotate-[2deg] border-4 border-cream">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/beer-garden-3.jpg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's beer garden" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        {# Front: bottom, overlaps middle #}
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute lg:-bottom-10 lg:left-[8%] lg:w-[42%] lg:h-[38%] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl rotate-[-1.5deg] border-4 border-cream">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/images/beer-garden-5.jpeg' | url }}" alt="Nadine's beer garden" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="relative overflow-hidden -mt-[120px] lg:mt-0">
    {# Background image #}
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/images/bar-1.jpg' | url }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-espresso/60"></div>
    </div>

    {# Content pushed right #}
    <div class="relative max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 pt-[280px] pb-20 lg:py-20 flex justify-end">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 bg-cream rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-10 fade-up">
        <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-3">Get in Touch</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl text-espresso mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
          <span class="text-amber">&#9670;</span>
          <span class="block w-12 h-px bg-amber/50"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          {# Telephone #}
          <div>
            <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-2">Telephone</p>
            <a href="tel:{{ client.phone }}" class="font-body text-espresso font-bold hover:text-amber transition-colors">{{ client.phone }}</a>
          </div>
          {# Follow Us #}
          <div>
            <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-2">Follow Us</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <a href="{{ client.social.facebook }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Facebook" class="text-espresso hover:text-amber transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987H7.898V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="{{ client.social.instagram }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Instagram" class="text-espresso hover:text-amber transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          {# Hours — full width #}
          <div class="col-span-2">
            <p class="font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber mb-2">Hours</p>
            <table class="w-full font-body text-sm text-espresso/70">
              {% for row in client.hours %}
              <tr>
                <td class="py-0.5 pr-6 font-bold text-espresso">{{ row.days }}</td>
                <td class="py-0.5">{{ row.time }}</td>
              </tr>
              {% endfor %}
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full h-px bg-espresso/10 mb-8"></div>

        <iframe src="https://88restaurants.com/799/contact_forms" frameborder="0" width="100%" height="545" scrolling="no"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}